OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWater firms want bill rises
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto cut leaks and spills    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Water companies in England and Wales   
OL,6, want bills to increase by #156 a year  
OL,7, by 2030 to pay for upgrades and reduce 
OL,8, sewage discharges.                     
OL,10,FThe increase would allow infrastructure
OL,11,Fspending to almost double to #96bn, the
OL,12,Fwater industry says.                   
OL,14,FBut the proposals come amid public     
OL,15,Fanger at the amount of sewage being    
OL,16,Fdischarged into rivers and seas and    
OL,17,Fcontinued cost of living pressures.    
OL,19,FWater industry regulator Ofwat has been
OL,20,Fasked to approve the plans.            
